# canonical-contract-registry.json

Required fields per entry:
- authRequired (boolean)
- category (form / read-model / webhook)
- dedupeKey (string)
- endpoint (absolute URL)
- id (lowercase snake_case)
- method (GET / POST / PATCH / PUT / DELETE)
- path (repo path to contract file)
- receiptKeyPattern (string)
- receiptSource (string)
- signatureRequired (boolean)
- status (active / deprecated / draft)
- usedOnPages (array of strings)
- version (integer, minimum 1)
- writes (array of collection names)